# Exercise 3/ Lab 2 - Rendezvous

This project shows an implementation of Rendezvous using custom Semaphore class

## Requirements
- Compatible with **Linux** only
- A C++11 compiler
- The MakeFile

## Install
2. Go to Exercises/ directory: cd Exercise Three_Rendezvous
3. Build project: make CLEAN && make
4. Run: ./rendezvous

## Project/files Content
- **Sempahore:** implementation of a Semaphore
- **main.cpp:** the traditional start point of the program, showing off the Rendezvous implementation

